@startuml UC-02-BookTrip-StateMachine
skinparam state {
    BackgroundColor<<error>> LightCoral
    BackgroundColor<<success>> LightGreen
}

[*] --> Idle : System Ready

Idle --> AwaitingInput : User initiates booking

AwaitingInput : Entry / Display booking form
AwaitingInput : Do / Collect traveler info\nand connection details
AwaitingInput --> ValidatingInput : User submits booking

ValidatingInput : Entry / Validate input data
ValidatingInput --> InputError <<error>> : Invalid data\n(missing fields,\ninvalid format)
ValidatingInput --> ValidatingRoutes : Input valid

InputError : Entry / Display error message
InputError --> AwaitingInput : User corrects input
InputError --> Idle : User cancels

ValidatingRoutes : Entry / Check route IDs exist
ValidatingRoutes --> RouteError <<error>> : Route ID not found
ValidatingRoutes --> ValidatingLayovers : All routes valid

RouteError : Entry / Display route error
RouteError --> AwaitingInput : User modifies routes
RouteError --> Idle : User cancels

ValidatingLayovers : Entry / Check layover policy
ValidatingLayovers : Do / Validate connection\nlayover durations
ValidatingLayovers --> LayoverError <<error>> : Policy violation\n(excessive layover)
ValidatingLayovers --> ProcessingTravelers : Layovers compliant

LayoverError : Entry / Display policy violation
LayoverError --> AwaitingInput : User selects different connection
LayoverError --> Idle : User cancels

ProcessingTravelers : Entry / Begin transaction
ProcessingTravelers : Do / Upsert traveler records
ProcessingTravelers --> CreatingTrip : Travelers saved

CreatingTrip : Entry / Create Trip entity
CreatingTrip : Do / Persist trip with routes
CreatingTrip --> LinkingTravelers : Trip created

LinkingTravelers : Entry / Associate travelers
LinkingTravelers : Do / Populate trip_travelers table
LinkingTravelers --> IssuingTickets : Travelers linked

IssuingTickets : Entry / Generate tickets
IssuingTickets : Do / Create one ticket per traveler\nwith issued timestamp
IssuingTickets --> CommittingTransaction : All tickets created

CommittingTransaction : Entry / Commit transaction
CommittingTransaction --> DatabaseError <<error>> : DB write failure
CommittingTransaction --> BookingComplete <<success>> : Transaction committed

DatabaseError : Entry / Rollback transaction
DatabaseError : Do / Log error
DatabaseError --> Idle : Display error / Retry

BookingComplete : Entry / Generate response
BookingComplete : Do / Return trip ID,\nticket IDs, success message
BookingComplete --> DisplayingConfirmation <<success>> : Response sent

DisplayingConfirmation : Entry / Show confirmation
DisplayingConfirmation : Do / Display trip details,\nticket numbers
DisplayingConfirmation --> Idle : User acknowledges

note right of ValidatingLayovers
  Policy Rules:
  - Daytime (06:00-22:00): max 2h layover
  - Nighttime (22:00-06:00): max 30min layover
end note

note right of IssuingTickets
  One ticket per traveler:
  - Links traveler to trip
  - Records issuedAt timestamp
  - Ensures no duplicates
end note
DisplayingConfirmation --> [*] : User acknowledges

@enduml
